{{!< default}}

{{#contentFor 'htmlLang'}}{{@site.locale}}{{/contentFor}}

{{#contentFor 'meta'}}
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
{{/contentFor}}

{{#contentFor 'styles'}}
    <link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='{{asset 'css/welcome.css'}}' />
{{/contentFor}}

{{#contentFor 'title'}}Thank you!! - {{meta_title}}{{/contentFor}}

<div class='mds-welcome'>
    <div class='mds-container'>
        {{#if @member.paid}}
            {{! Logged in }}
            <header class='mds-header'>
                <div>
                    <h1>Thank you for subscribing!</h1>
                </div>
            </header>

            <section class='mds-welcome-content'>
                {{> "images/welcome"}}
                <p class='mds-welcome-description'>
                    Hey! Thank you so much for subscribing to my blog.
                    As it is <strong>a completely independent publication</strong>, each subscription means the world to me.
                    I hope you'll find it worth the money you spent.
                </p>
                <p class='mds-welcome-description'>
                    You now have full access to the library of blog posts and newsletter issues.
                    You'll receive each new issue straight into you inbox. You'll also get a notification email for each new blog post I publish.
                    If it's not already done, please join
                    <a href="https://community.mindsers.blog" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">the Mindsers Blog Private Club</a> (our discord community server)!
                    I can't wait to talk with you about the content but also about your own journey as a
                    developer/entrepreneur.
                </p>
                <p class='mds-welcome-description'>
                    Also, if you like what I try to create here or have any ideas on how to improve it,
                    <strong>can you please send me your feedbacks?</strong> I would love to read them!
                </p>
                <p class='mds-welcome-link'>
                    <a class='button' href='/posts/'>
                        Read the blog posts
                    </a>
                    <a class='button primary' href='/issues/'>
                        Read the previous issues
                    </a>
                </p>

            </section>

        {{else}}
            {{! Not logged in: Redirect to signin }}
            <script>window.location = '{{@site.url}}/login/';</script>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
</div>